title: Doctor Who - The Tenth Planet
description:
The final story arc of the first Doctor as he faces down the Cybermen.

Since footage of the fourth episode was lost, an entirely new animated episode was created with the surviving audio files.

Of note is the Doctor's last words, "this old body is wearing thin..." echoed fifty years later by the War Doctor as he dies and changes into the 10th.

Transcoded directly to MKV from the original DVD files.
